OL,3,CDemolition of crumbling Gateshead
OL,4,CFlyover due to start
OL,6,FDemolition of the Gateshead Flyover
OL,7,Fwill start today.
OL,9,FContractors are at last going to begin
OL,10,Ftearing down the crumbling concrete
OL,11,Fhighway, which has been closed since
OL,12,FDecember 2024 because of safety fears.
OL,14,FFrustration has built over the ongoing
OL,15,Fpresence of the A167 flyover, which
OL,16,Fruns around the edge of Gateshead town
OL,17,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
