OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776777070
OL,3,CDemolition of crumbling Gateshead
OL,4,CFlyover due to start
OL,6,FBut Monday (20 April) will offer the
OL,7,Ffirst glimpse of the main span of the
OL,8,Felevated highway, under which huge
OL,9,Fsteel props have now been erected,
OL,10,Fstarting to come down.
OL,12,F'Nibbling' machines will gradually eat
OL,13,Faway at the 1970s structure over the
OL,14,Fcoming months, with the hope being
OL,15,Fthat its removal will be complete by
OL,16,FOctober this year, the Local Democracy
OL,17,FReporting Service reports.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
