CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776777070
OL,3,CDemolition of crumbling Gateshead
OL,4,CFlyover due to start
OL,6,FThe on and off ramps in the centre of
OL,7,Fthe flyover, just to the south of the
OL,8,FSunderland Road bus lane, will be the
OL,9,Ffirst elements demolished.
OL,11,FIt follows the demolition of the
OL,12,Fneighbouring Computer House office
OL,13,Fblock.
OL,15,FOnce the ramps are removed, focus will
OL,16,Fmove to the section of the flyover
OL,17,Fdirectly above the Sunderland Road bus
OL,18,Flane, and then further south towards
OL,19,FFive Bridges roundabout around June.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
