PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776777070
OL,3,CDemolition of crumbling Gateshead
OL,4,CFlyover due to start
OL,6,FSome works will take place around the
OL,7,FPark Lane roundabout in May in
OL,8,Fpreparation for that area of the
OL,9,Fhighway to be removed, but the actual
OL,10,Fdemolition there will be during the
OL,11,Fsummer.
OL,13,FThe last section of the work, in the
OL,14,Fearly autumn, will be on the areas
OL,15,Fdirectly above the underground Tyne
OL,16,Fand Wear Metro tunnels.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
