PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776777070
OL,3,CDemolition of crumbling Gateshead
OL,4,CFlyover due to start
OL,6,FConcerns that the flyover was at risk
OL,7,Fof collapse led to all Metro services
OL,8,Facross the River Tyne to be suspended
OL,9,Fin late 2024, causing a travel crisis
OL,10,Feither side of Christmas.
OL,12,FThe full impact of the demolition
OL,13,Fworks on the underground Metro tunnels
OL,14,Fis not yet certain, though Gateshead
OL,15,FCouncil bosses hope that they will not
OL,16,Fhave to be closed again.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
