CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776777070
OL,3,CDemolition of crumbling Gateshead
OL,4,CFlyover due to start
OL,6,FScott Beattie, operations manager at
OL,7,Fcontractors BAM said last month:
OL,8,F"Safety and minimising disruption are
OL,9,Fat the heart of our approach. We're
OL,10,Finstalling protective screens, have
OL,11,Festablished dedicated haul roads, and
OL,12,Fput in place robust traffic and
OL,13,Fpedestrian management plans.
OL,15,F"We are working closely with Gateshead
OL,16,FCouncil to keep the town moving as
OL,17,Feffectively as possible whilst the
OL,18,Fdemolition takes place.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
