OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776777070
OL,3,CDemolition of crumbling Gateshead
OL,4,CFlyover due to start
OL,6,F"With our partners, we are committed
OL,7,Fto delivering this complex project
OL,8,Fwhile supporting the wider
OL,9,Fregeneration of the town."
OL,11,FThe council has previously pledged in
OL,12,FMarch last year that the flyover would
OL,13,Fbe gone "within a year", before the
OL,14,Flocal authority later said that it
OL,15,Fwould be largely demolished by May
OL,16,F2026.
OL,18,FThat target end date has now been
OL,19,Fpushed back to the autumn of this year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@ZO]uD@IOUuD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
